{"TopicId":139049,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"Help with Kerbiting Planets!","CreatedByName":"WolfyDoo","CreatedById":148179,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-05T15:10:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"WolfyDoo","CreatedById":148179,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-05T15:10:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo everything is explained in a video I made.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope somebody knows why it happens and I hope somebody can tell me how to fix the problem!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVideo:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/f9qVHZthlWw?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MrHappyFace","CreatedById":76365,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-05T16:37:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMods that reparent kerbin (set it\u0027s parent body to something other than the sun) are inherently glitchy because of the way KSP\u0027s planets work internally.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt seems this bug doesn\u0027t adversely affect gameplay and\u00A0it\u0027s just a visual glitch, so I wouldn\u0027t worry about it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WolfyDoo","CreatedById":148179,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-05T16:44:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh, okay! Thanks a lot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}